Pseudocymopterus.

Element (1) incorporates morphological traits of both V. myrtillus (VAMY) & V. scoparium (VASC).

locality: Mosquito Range, San Isabel National Forest, headwaters of Lynch Creek below saddle W. of W. Buffalo Peak.
georeferenceRemarks: I plotted the UTM at the collector provided UTM in section 16. RA
